## Clang-based Software Hint Insertion

### Building
Prequisites: You must have `clang`, including `clang-dev` and `llvm` installed (these are both installable via `apt`). We used `llvm-18` for development, though any modern release should work. 

`mkdir build`

`cd build`

`cmake ..`

`make`

This will produce a binary named `ezh_clang_hints`. 

### Usage
`./ezh_clang_hints <source>`
